{"word":"H3302 - יָפָה - yâphâh - yaw-faw' - Be beautiful","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">יָפָה</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>yâphâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>yaw-faw'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Be beautiful"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - இன்பமாயிரு, அழகாயிரு. அழகுபடுத்து, அழகுள்ளவள், இன்பமுள்ளவள், அலங்காரமாயிரு, சவுந்தரியமுள்ளவர், அலங்கரி"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to be bright, to be beautiful, to be handsome, to be fair"},{"paragraph":"a) (Qal) to be beautiful"},{"paragraph":"b) (Piel) to beautify"},{"paragraph":"c) (Pual) to be beautiful"},{"paragraph":"d) (Hithpael) to beautify oneself"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; properly to <i>be bright</i>, that is, (by implication) <i>beautiful: - </i>be beautiful, be (make self) fair (-r), deck."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3302 - יָפָה - yâphâh - yaw-faw'/3302\">H3302</a>, <a href=\"#/H3303 - יָפֶה - yâpheh - yaw-feh'/3303\">H3303</a>, <a href=\"#/H3304 - יְפֵה־פִיָּה - yᵉphêh-phîyâh - yef-eh' fee-yaw'/3304\">H3304</a>, <a href=\"#/H3305 - יָפֹו - Yâphôw - yaw-fo'/3305\">H3305</a>, <a href=\"#/H3308 - יֳפִי - yŏphîy - yof-ee'/3308\">H3308</a>"}]}